Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.16,0:00:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Like a cruel angel{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.13,0:00:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Become a legend, young boy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.98,0:00:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When a blue wind{\i0}\N{\i1}Knocks on the door to your heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.73,0:00:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You just gaze back at me{\i0}\N{\i1}And smile oh so gently{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.66,0:00:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So eager for something{\i0}\N{\i1}You touch so softly{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.75,0:00:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those innocent eyes{\i0}\N{\i1}Know nothing of the fate that awaits{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.34,0:00:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But one day, you will realize{\i0}\N{\i1}That upon your back{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.76,0:01:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You have wings{\i0}\N{\i1}You can fly to the faraway future{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.23,0:01:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The cruel angel's thesis{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.94,0:01:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One day, you'll take off through a window{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.70,0:01:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If your overflowing pathos{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.45,0:01:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Leads you to betray your memories{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.20,0:01:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then embrace the heavens and shine bright{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.87,0:01:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Become legend, young boy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.63,0:01:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hey, have you seen her?\N-I sure have!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.38,0:01:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,-Seen who?\N-Haven't you heard about the foreigner?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.51,0:01:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Foreigner?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.80,0:01:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, she transferred into\N8th Grade Class A! Last week!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.68,0:01:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she hot or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.64,0:01:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,PHOTO PRINTS, 30 YEN EACH!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.81,0:01:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard her name is Asuka Langley Soryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.94,0:01:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, she's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.40,0:01:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,She grew up overseas, right?\NI wonder if she, um, matured early.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.24,0:02:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't get it! I bet she went through\Na rough breakup back in Germany!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.99,0:02:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,She's in a strange land\Nwith her heart still broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.25,0:02:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody's talking about her...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.80,0:02:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,"Asuka" this and "Asuka" that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.34,0:02:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,-If only they knew.\N-Pleasure doing business!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.68,0:02:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad her personality\Ndoesn't show up in these pictures...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.97,0:02:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hello, Shinji!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.85,0:02:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Guten Morgen!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.65,0:02:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Gooten morgun...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.61,0:02:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, you look all mopey,\Nand it's first thing in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.52,0:02:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I did you the favor of talking to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.78,0:02:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So maybe you could try to look happy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.11,0:02:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,She's here, right? The other one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.24,0:02:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Other what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.33,0:02:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of idiot are you?\NI mean the First Children! Who else?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.00,0:02:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you mean Ayanami. She's...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.84,0:03:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hello!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.80,0:03:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're Rei Ayanami,\Nthe prototype's pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.64,0:03:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Asuka. Asuka Langley Soryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.60,0:03:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva-02's pilot. Let's be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.98,0:03:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.36,0:03:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's best for everyone that way.\NFor various reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.99,0:03:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be your friend if I'm ordered to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.24,0:03:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a strange one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.78,0:03:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, is it just weirdos\Nthat get picked as Eva pilots?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.88,0:03:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,-I think you've lost some weight.\N-Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.42,0:03:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,-You're in love, but it will end in tears.\N-Really? And just how do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.64,0:03:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Because people with a mole along where\Ntears flow are doomed to a life of tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.69,0:03:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this your opening seduction move?\NI wouldn't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.77,0:03:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a mean old lady\Nlooking right at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.03,0:04:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's been a long time, Ryoji.\N-That it has.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.57,0:04:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I must say, you're off your game.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.62,0:04:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just as stupid as he ever was!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.12,0:04:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You've finished overseeing the handover\Nof Unit 02, so go home already!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.00,0:04:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,New orders came in this morning.\NI'm here until further notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.75,0:04:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The three of us, together again.\NIt will be just like old times!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.05,0:04:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Together with you?! Dream on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.34,0:04:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,An Angel attack?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.80,0:04:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Report from cruiser{\i0} Haruna {\i1}in patrol.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.56,0:04:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Large submerged object encountered{\i0}\N{\i1}off coast of Kii Peninsula.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.52,0:04:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Relaying data."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.89,0:04:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Cross-checking received data.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.02,0:04:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wavelength pattern, blue.\NConfirmed as Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.27,0:04:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,All personnel,\Ncondition one battle stations!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.78,0:04:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokyo-3's intercept systems\Nwere badly damaged
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.53,0:04:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,in the last attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.29,0:04:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We're only back up to 26% capacity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.37,0:04:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,In actual combat, that's effectively zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.92,0:04:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,As such,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.59,0:05:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,we're going to hit it just before\Nit comes ashore this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.30,0:05:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Units 01 and 02 will\Nengage the target in turns
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.30,0:05:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,in close-quarters combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.72,0:05:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}-Roger.{\i0}\N{\i1}-Roger.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.85,0:05:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my debut battle in Japan.\NWhy won't she let me fight it on my own?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.56,0:05:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It can't be helped. This is her plan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.31,0:05:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Just so we're clear, don't do anything\Nthat will cramp my style, got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.53,0:05:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Um, okay...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.28,0:05:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Why was somebody like {\i1}him{\i0}\Nchosen to be a pilot?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.17,0:05:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like this two-on-one stuff.\NIt seems like cheating.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.59,0:05:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not my thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.59,0:05:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We don't have the luxury of choice.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.39,0:05:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We do what we have to do to survive.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.81,0:05:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.06,0:06:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Commence attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.73,0:06:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go first, then! Cover me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.28,0:06:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-Cover you?!\N{\i1}-Ladies first!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.07,0:06:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, you don't have to be so bossy.\NI was here first...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.12,0:06:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.84,0:06:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm impressed...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.72,0:06:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,See that, Third Children?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.93,0:06:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,A battle should be quick and clean!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.87,0:06:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's playing dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.25,0:07:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At 10:58:15 a.m., Unit 01{\i0}\N{\i1}was attacked by Target Alpha,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.08,0:07:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}half of the original target{\i0}\N{\i1}that had split in two,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.80,0:07:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and was flung two kilometers{\i0}\N{\i1}into Suruga Bay, where it sank.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.97,0:07:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At 10:58:20 a.m., Unit 02 was{\i0}\N{\i1}rendered inoperative by Target Bravo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.30,0:07:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Project E Director{\i0}\N{\i1}had the following to say:{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.64,0:07:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How appalling.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.02,0:07:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,My precious debut fight\Ngot ruined because of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.94,0:07:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about? It happened\Nbecause you pulled that dumb stunt!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.94,0:07:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Dumb stunt?! How does a wimp like you\Nget to talk to me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.36,0:07:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got some nerve!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.65,0:07:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! This mess happened because\Nyou were in such a rush to beat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.32,0:07:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at yours, it's like a drowned--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.87,0:07:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At 11:03 a.m.,{\i0}\N{\i1}Nerv halted further operations.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.83,0:07:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Command was transferred{\i0}\N{\i1}to the UN Second Army Group.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.00,0:07:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Those two made us look like fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.46,0:07:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At 11:05 a.m., the target was hit{\i0}\N{\i1}with an N2 mine.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.84,0:07:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have to revise the maps again...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.80,0:07:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It succeeded in incinerating{\i0}\N{\i1}28% of their mass.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.60,0:07:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,-Is it dead?\N-No, only delayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.39,0:08:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It will resume its advance eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.81,0:08:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we should count our blessings\Nthat it bought us time to regroup.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.73,0:08:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.69,0:08:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand what your job here is?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.32,0:08:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-To pilot the Evas.\N-No! It's to defeat the Angels!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.70,0:08:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Nerv does not exist in order\Nto make buffoons of ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.74,0:08:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,To do your job,\Nyou must work together to--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.99,0:08:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Work with this jerk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.95,0:08:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.87,0:08:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does everyone here\Nget angry so easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.04,0:08:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Adults don't like being made to look bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.63,0:08:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, where is Ms. Misato?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.22,0:08:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,On aftermath detail. It's the job of\Nthe person in charge to take the heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.80,0:08:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Complaints and damage assessments\Nfrom all related agencies.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.93,0:08:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is the bill from the UN.\NComplaints from Public Affairs, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.69,0:08:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you go through them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.44,0:08:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I already know what they're going to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.82,0:08:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,"If you're going to fight,\Ndo it in Tokyo-3!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.45,0:08:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Very perceptive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.90,0:08:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't need to tell me that. Once that\Nwreck is dealt with, we'll fight here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.74,0:09:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll defeat that Angel, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.41,0:09:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The Deputy Commander is furious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.58,0:09:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If you make him look bad again,\Nhe'll demote you, mark my words.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.42,0:09:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess the one silver lining\Nis that Commander Ikari isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.00,0:09:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He would fire you on the spot.\NEven without seeing this pile.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.55,0:09:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you come bearing ideas\Nthat will save my hide, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.72,0:09:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No, just the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.39,0:09:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my Dr. Ritsuko Akagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.60,0:09:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Good old friends are great blessings!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.35,0:09:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm flattered, but I'm not\Nthe old friend who's saving your hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.44,0:09:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Ryoji's idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.69,0:09:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryoji's?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.69,0:09:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,TO MY HONEY
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.66,0:09:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,DHU\NARTA MOVING CENTER
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.79,0:09:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.37,0:09:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that anybody's here\Nto hear me say it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.51,0:09:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What is all this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.72,0:09:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be rude! Those are my things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.93,0:10:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What are you doing here, Soryu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.89,0:10:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'm surprised you're still here.\N-What do you mean, "still"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.02,0:10:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You got sacked today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.48,0:10:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be Misato's roommate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.65,0:10:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, considering which of us is better,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.90,0:10:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,it's the natural choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.74,0:10:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Admittedly, I'd rather be\Nliving with Mr. Kaji.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.28,0:10:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,How come Japanese rooms are so small?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.33,0:10:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I could only fit half of my stuff in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.29,0:10:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,SHINJI'S ROO--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.62,0:10:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And how come Japanese people\Nhave zero sense of caution?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.13,0:10:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you live in a house\Nwith rooms that don't have locks?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.01,0:10:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.92,0:10:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because we Japanese try to be\Nperceptive and considerate of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.59,0:10:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,-Ms. Misato!\N-Misato!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.76,0:10:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home. You two seem\Nto be off to a good start already!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.06,0:10:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.43,0:10:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Preparing for our next battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.39,0:10:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.35,0:10:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The 7th Angel has just one weakness!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.73,0:10:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,A two-point attack to its core unit\Nwhile it's divided in two.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.19,0:10:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.49,0:10:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.07,0:11:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,it has to be a perfectly\Ncoordinated attack by both Evas.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.41,0:11:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And to do that, it's essential that\Nyou two work in perfect unison.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.95,0:11:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,To that end, you two are going\Nto live here together, starting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.17,0:11:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! They say boys and girls mustn't\Nsleep in the same room after age seven!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.17,0:11:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The Angel is regenerating as we speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.43,0:11:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It will attack again in six days.\NWe don't have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.76,0:11:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This is ridiculous...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.81,0:11:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, here is how we turn\Nthe ridiculous into the possible:
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.81,0:11:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,To achieve perfect unison,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.39,0:11:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,you're going to memorize\Nan attack pattern that's set to this song.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.48,0:11:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You have six days to do it.\NThe sooner, the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.36,0:11:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Humph!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.70,0:11:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what's up with Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.12,0:11:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he's missed school\Nthree days in a row.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.30,0:11:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's the Class Rep.\N-It's two thirds of the Idiot Trio.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.17,0:12:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So what are {\i1}you{\i0} doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.47,0:12:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here to check in on Ms. Soryu.\NWhat are you two doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.80,0:12:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Checking in on Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.10,0:12:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you stopping here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.89,0:12:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-Coming!\N-Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.36,0:12:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You dirty traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.57,0:12:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,They're wearing matching outfits again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.11,0:12:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Rubs me the wrong way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.32,0:12:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Misato says that Japanese start\Nwith the form and the rest will follow,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.99,0:12:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,so she's forcing us to wear this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.00,0:12:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This is so indecent! Both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.08,0:12:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not what you think!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.79,0:12:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it must be even worse!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.29,0:12:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.34,0:12:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you mind explaining this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.76,0:12:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You should have just said so\Nin the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.97,0:12:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So, is the unison training going well?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.52,0:12:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,See for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.27,0:12:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you expect?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.73,0:13:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's never going to work if I have to\Nforce myself down to Shinji's level!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.53,0:13:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This whole thing is flat-out impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.95,0:13:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you want out?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.45,0:13:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no one else, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.45,0:13:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-Rei?\N-Yes, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.08,0:13:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-Give it a try.\N-Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.55,0:13:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,From the looks of it, it might be better\Nto change the plan and use Rei instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.39,0:13:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Screw this! I'm out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.73,0:13:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,-Ms. Asuka!\N-"Even a demon's eyes can shed tears."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.44,0:13:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.82,0:13:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Go after her!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.99,0:13:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You made a girl cry!\NGet out there and make it right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.92,0:14:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,-Um...\N-Don't say anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.51,0:14:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, I have to do this.\NPiloting the Eva is all I've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.14,0:14:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.15,0:14:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what it takes,\NI'm gonna get back at Rei and Misato!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.11,0:14:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back at them? For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.23,0:14:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so clueless all the time?!\NYou call yourself a man?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.99,0:14:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,They're gonna... pay for wounding\Nmy pride! With interest!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.13,0:14:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,TWO DAYS LEFT
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.44,0:15:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,ATTACK TOMORROW
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.74,0:15:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-Where's Misato?\N-At work.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.87,0:15:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She called and said\Nshe'll be there all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.00,0:15:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. That means it's just\Nyou and me here tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.51,0:15:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This doorway is the impenetrable\NWall of Jericho!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.89,0:15:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.27,0:15:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Putting so much as a toe\Nover this line is a capital offense!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.02,0:15:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't stay up past your bedtime, baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.23,0:15:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,How can Japanese people\Nsleep on the stupid floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.24,0:15:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.81,0:17:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Mommy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.81,0:17:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Mommy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.36,0:17:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just as much a kid as I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.99,0:17:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't! We're being watched!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.53,0:17:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-Who's watching?\N-Who do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.60,0:17:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, we're not involved anymore.\NDon't do that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.85,0:17:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But your lips didn't tell me to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.65,0:17:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Which should I believe?\NYour lips or your words?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.63,0:18:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.47,0:18:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.97,0:18:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not drinking tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.22,0:18:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yeah, well...\N-So, which is it? Work? Or a man?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.35,0:18:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A little of both.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.15,0:18:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder, is the attraction still there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.98,0:18:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.86,0:18:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I'd still have feelings\Nfor a jerk like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.45,0:18:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I can blame it on being young and foolish,\Nbut being in a relationship with that guy
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.62,0:18:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,is the biggest regret I have in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.20,0:18:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I was talking about Ryoji's feelings.\NDid that catch you off guard?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.04,0:18:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, look here--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.38,0:18:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting angry only proves my point.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.25,0:18:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Try being more honest\Nwith yourself this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.76,0:18:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Things are different from eight years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.09,0:19:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing has changed. Not one bit.\NHe hasn't grown up at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.01,0:19:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, back to work!\NTomorrow is the big day!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.74,0:19:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Target has breached\NGoura Absolute Defense Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.87,0:19:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.66,0:19:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We're ready for you this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.62,0:19:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Raise your A.T. Fields{\i0}\N{\i1}as soon as the music starts.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.71,0:19:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Follow the plan from there.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.38,0:19:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Got that, you two?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.09,0:19:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,-{\i1}Roger!{\i0}\N-{\i1}Roger!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.71,0:19:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Target has entered the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.84,0:19:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up! We're going balls to the wall,\Nfull speed ahead from the get-go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.63,0:19:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. We'll finish this in 62 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.72,0:19:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-Target is about to reach Point Zero!\N-Jettison external power plugs!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.02,0:19:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.27,0:19:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,TIME REMAINING
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.88,0:21:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Both Evas accounted for!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.18,0:21:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-Oh, geez...\N-How appalling.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.81,0:21:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, what do you think{\i0}\N{\i1}you're doing to my Unit 02?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.19,0:21:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! You're the one\Nwho came barreling into {\i1}me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.15,0:21:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're the one who lost{\i0}\N{\i1}the beat at the end!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.03,0:21:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You have your head{\i0}\N{\i1}up your ass all the time!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.07,0:21:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And what were you doing{\i0}\N{\i1}last night instead of sleeping?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.62,0:21:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was doing visualization training{\i0}\N{\i1}for today's battle!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.00,0:21:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're full of it! I know you tried{\i0}\N{\i1}to kiss me while I was sleeping!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.75,0:21:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No way! You were awake?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.29,0:21:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's horrible!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.50,0:21:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I said that as a joke,{\i0}\N{\i1}but you really did? You kissed me?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.72,0:21:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't! I stopped myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.51,0:21:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pervert! Weirdo! Freak!{\i0}\N{\i1}I can't believe you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.55,0:21:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're the one who sleepwalked over{\i0}\N{\i1}and started talking in your sleep!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.89,0:21:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,They're making us look like fools again...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.06,0:22:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,TO BE CONTINUED
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.59,0:23:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}An unhatched Angel slumbers{\i0}\N{\i1}within the crater of Mt. Asama.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.30,0:23:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nerv attempts their{\i0}\N{\i1}first capture of an Angel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.89,0:23:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Outfitted for localized combat,{\i0}\N{\i1}Eva-02 plunges into a red-hot hell.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.39,0:23:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Next episode! "The Magma Diver"!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.85,0:23:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tune in next time{\i0}\N{\i1}for lots more fan service!{\i0}
